## Global

- TypeScript strict ONLY
- No `any`
- No console.log
- No inline styles
- No CSS Modules
- No styled-components

## React / Next.js

- Server Components by default
- "use client" allowed ONLY for:
  forms, filters, modals, sliders, maps
- One h1 per page
- next/image required for all images
- width, height, sizes are mandatory

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS only
- Use cn() for class merging
- No custom CSS files

## i18n

- NO hardcoded strings
- All text via t("key")
- Locale-prefixed routes ONLY
- Never rename or delete translation keys

## Animation

- Framer Motion is FORBIDDEN
- Allowed: CSS transitions, tailwindcss-animate, AOS

## CMS

- Sanity queries must be typed
- No untyped GROQ results
- Locale-aware content only

## Git

- Enforce conventional commits
- No direct commits to main
